      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Each patent is now represented as a sequence of integers. Let's look at an example of a few features and the corresponding labels. The label is the next word in the sequence after the first 50 words."
